<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>AutoIA - Tu Negocio Nunca Duerme</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        :root {
            --bg-primary: #000000;
            --bg-secondary: #111111;
            --text-primary: #ffffff;
            --text-secondary: #86868b;
            --accent: #2997ff;
            --gray: #1d1d1f;
        }

        html {
            scroll-behavior: smooth;
        }

        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: var(--bg-primary);
            color: var(--text-primary);
            overflow-x: hidden;
            line-height: 1.47059;
            font-weight: 400;
            letter-spacing: -0.022em;
        }

        nav {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 48px;
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8);
            backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
            z-index: 9999;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        }

        .nav-content {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 1024px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }

        .logo {
            font-size: 21px;
            font-weight: 600;
            letter-spacing: -0.5px;
        }

        .logo span {
            font-weight: 300;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
        }

        .nav-links {
            display: flex;
            gap: 40px;
            list-style: none;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
        }

        .nav-links a {
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: color 0.3s;
        }

        .nav-links a:hover {
            color: var(--text-primary);
        }

        .hero {
            height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            background: var(--bg-primary);
        }

        .hero-content {
            z-index: 2;
            opacity: 0;
            transform: translateY(30px);
            animation: fadeInUp 1.5s ease-out forwards;
        }

        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 96px;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: -0.015em;
            line-height: 1.05;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            background: linear-gradient(180deg, #fff 0%, #999 100%);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        }

        .hero .subtitle {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 400;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            opacity: 0;
            animation: fadeInUp 1.5s ease-out 0.3s forwards;
        }

        .hero .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: var(--accent);
            color: white;
            padding: 18px 40px;
            border-radius: 50px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 17px;
            font-weight: 500;
            opacity: 0;
            animation: fadeInUp 1.5s ease-out 0.6s forwards;
            transition: transform 0.3s, box-shadow 0.3s;
        }

        .hero .cta-button:hover {
            transform: scale(1.05);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(41, 151, 255, 0.3);
        }

        .hero .secondary-link {
            display: block;
            margin-top: 20px;
            color: var(--accent);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 19px;
            opacity: 0;
            animation: fadeInUp 1.5s ease-out 0.9s forwards;
        }

        .hero .secondary-link:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        .scroll-indicator {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 40px;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            animation: bounce 2s infinite;
            opacity: 0.5;
        }

        @keyframes bounce {
            0%, 20%, 50%, 80%, 100% { transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(0); }
            40% { transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(-10px); }
            60% { transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(-5px); }
        }

        .section {
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 100px 20px;
            position: relative;
            background: var(--bg-primary);
        }

        .section.sticky {
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
        }

        .section-content {
            max-width: 980px;
            width: 100%;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .section h2 {
            font-size: 80px;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: -0.015em;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            line-height: 1.1;
        }

        .section h3 {
            font-size: 40px;
            font-weight: 600;
            letter-spacing: -0.015em;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: var(--text-primary);
        }

        .section p {
            font-size: 21px;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto 40px;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        .services-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 30px;
            max-width: 1200px;
            width: 100%;
            margin-top: 60px;
        }

        .service-card {
            background: var(--gray);
            border-radius: 24px;
            padding: 50px 40px;
            text-align: left;
            transition: transform 0.5s, box-shadow 0.5s;
            opacity: 0;
            transform: translateY(50px);
        }

        .service-card.visible {
            opacity: 1;
            transform: translateY(0);
        }

        .service-card:hover {
            transform: scale(1.02);
            box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
        }

        .service-icon {
            font-size: 48px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .service-card h4 {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .service-card p {
            font-size: 17px;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            text-align: left;
        }

        .price {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--text-primary);
        }

        .price span {
            font-size: 15px;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            font-weight: 400;
        }

        .features-list {
            list-style: none;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 60px auto;
        }

        .features-list li {
            font-size: 24px;
            padding: 30px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--gray);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 20px;
            opacity: 0;
            transform: translateX(-30px);
            transition: all 0.6s;
        }

        .features-list li.visible {
            opacity: 1;
            transform: translateX(0);
        }

        .features-list li::before {
            content: '✅';
            color: var(--accent);
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 28px;
        }

        /* RESTO DEL CSS SIN CAMBIOS */
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <nav>
        <div class="nav-content">
            <div class="logo">Auto<span>IA</span></div>
            <ul class="nav-links">
                <li><a href="#servicios">Servicios</a></li>
                <li><a href="#como-funciona">Cómo Funciona</a></li>
                <li><a href="#demo">Demo</a></li>
                <li><a href="#faq">FAQ</a></li>
                <li><a href="#contacto">Contacto</a></li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <section class="hero">
        <div class="hero-content">
            <h1>Tu Recepcionista<br>Inteligente</h1>
            <p class="subtitle">Nunca pierdas otra cita. Atiende clientes 24/7<br>automáticamente por WhatsApp.</p>
            <a href="#servicios" class="cta-button">Descubre cómo</a>
            <a href="#demo" class="secondary-link">Ver demo en vivo ></a>
        </div>
    </section>

